-- Finland's Konecranes Says It Has Contacted Demag About `Potential' Merger
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2010-10-08T15:16:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-08/finland-s-konecranes-says-it-has-contacted-demag-about-potential-merger.html
Konecranes Oyj said it has contacted
Germany’s Demag Cranes AG to “discuss a potential combination
of the two companies.” Demag has responded that is has “no
interest in engaging in any dialogue regarding such a potential
combination,” Konecranes said in a statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
